In [[Switzerland]], '''''Conseil d'État''''' is the name of the council constituting the cantonal government of French-speaking [[Cantons of Switzerland|canton]]s. It is not to be confused with the ''Conseil des États'' (or [[Swiss Council of States|Council of ''States'']]) which is a chamber of the Swiss parliament.

