{{Infobox ethnic group |group=Mono, Amono |image= |population=approximately 145,000 |popplace=[[Democratic Republic of Congo]] |rels=[[Christianity]] |langs=[[Mono language (Congo)]] }}
The '''Mono people''' are a [[Sub-Sahara]]n people of the [[Sudan]]ic cluster residing on land adjacent to the northwestern border of the [[Democratic Republic of Congo]].
